<id>1</id>
<lefticon>solo</lefticon>
<righticon>research</righticon>
<column>OOC</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Students watch the ﬁrst episode of a tv drama (ex. Madmen) that exposes them to assumptions about social interactions and hierarchies in the workplace.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
<linkedwf>undefined</linkedwf>
