<righticon>problem</righticon>
<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Students identify the higher and lower paying jobs and compare their categorizing to what they discussed regarding gender stereotyping in each job. They look for patterns with regards to these gender stereotypes and the way jobs are valued.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
